Disease: The type of disease or health condition the individual is experiencing
Fever: Whether the individual has a fever (Yes/No)
Cough: Whether the individual has a cough (Yes/No)
Fatigue: Whether the individual is experiencing fatigue (Yes/No)
Difficulty Breathing: Whether the individual is experiencing difficulty breathing (Yes/No)
Blood Pressure: The blood pressure level of the individual (Low/Normal)
Cholesterol Level: The cholesterol level of the individual (Normal/Abnormal)
Outcome Variable: The final outcome of the individual's health condition (Positive/Negative)
